sent.orig: You successfully killed 20 players with a pistol in a death match.
sent.trans: 在死亡比赛中成功使用手枪杀死20名对手。

sent.orig: It was the key that how to propagandize Microsoft technology and carry out technical activities successfully.
sent.trans: 如何更好的宣传微软的技术，更顺利的开展技术类的活动，是我们的重点所在。

sent.orig: Restaurants lobbied successfully to be exempted from nutritional labeling.
sent.trans: 餐厅成功地游说政府，不用标示自己产品的营养成份资讯。

sent.orig: The calculation results are successfully applied into Tarim oil field.
sent.trans: 计算结果在现场钻井中符合较好。

sent.orig: Biodegradable ethanolamine-plasticized tapioca starch (EPTS) was successfully prepared from plasticizer ethanolamine and tapioca starch.
sent.trans: 用乙醇胺对木薯淀粉进行塑化，制备了乙醇胺塑化木薯淀粉(EPTS)可生物分解材料。
